Config Sublime-text for anaconda3 in ubuntu
Tools ->New Build System...
--> input json code:
{
    "cmd": ["/home/ubuntu/anaconda3/bin/python", "-u", "$file"],
    "file_regex": "^[ ]*File \"(...*?)\", line ([0-9]*)",
    "selector": "source.python"
}

-->rename & save for example anaconda3
--> Select Tools --> Build System--> anaconda3
completed!

